item.title: Katee Sackhoff Says ‘The Mandalorian’ Ruined Her Confidence: “It Broke Me”
item.description: After voicing the animated version of Bo-Katan for years, Sackhoff said she struggled with the character on Disney+’s live-action version: “It destroyed my confidence.”
